text: The smoky jungle frog (Leptodactylus pentadactylus) is a species of frog in the family Leptodactylidae. It is found in Bolivia, Brazil, Colombia, Ecuador, Costa Rica, Panama, France, and Peru.Leptodactylus pentadactylus, AmphibiaWeb ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Smoky jungle frog
